data.description: ABSOLUTELY AMAZING SPACIOUS 4 BEDROOM SINGLE FAMILY HOME! ENTER INTO THIS GEM OF A HOME INTO A FLOWING OPEN FLOOR CONCEPT WITH GLEAMING HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT THE MAIN LEVEL. MAIN LEVEL CONSISTS OF THREE BEDROOMS AND A FULL BATHROOM WITH MODERN FINISHES. BEAUTIFUL WHITE KITCHEN WHIT QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS AND LOTS OF COUNTERSPACE. BASEMENT CONSISTS OF A HUGE RECREATIONAL/ FAMILY ROOM, ONE BEDROOM, LAUNDRY AREA AND A FULL MODERN BATHROOM. WALK OUTSIDE AND ENJOY A BBQ OR A BONFIRE IN THE BACK YARD. TWO CAR GARAGE WITH A HUGE DRIVEWAY FOR UP TP FIVE CARS. CLOSE TO SHOPPING CENTER, RESTAURANTS AND TRANSPORTATION. ALL APPLIANCES WILL BE STAYING INCLUDING A WASHER AND DRYER. COME AND MAKE THIS YOUR HOME!
